Title: Hung Out to Dry
Plot: During a training exercise, a marine's parachute fails to open and he crashes into a parked car where two teenagers were making out.  The NCIS team heads to the scene and has to determine if the marine's death was accidental or a murder.
GuestStars: Patrick Labyorteaux, James MacDonald, Rick Pasqualone, Dave Power, Chaney Kley, Keith Diamond, Julie Gonzalo, Brandon Davis, Pancho, Demmings, Lee Reherman
